msg: Fixing continuous checking of snapshot repos when requested metadata doesn't exist on the remote side.

author: dblevins
msg: Repackaged all code to the same package name.  Bought the name org.superbiz to use instead of org.acme or org.apache.openejb so the examples only use the word "openejb" where the must and users don't have to worry about which "openejb"s they can change and which must stay.
Made all pom artifactIds match the directories they live in.
Striped the headers out of the "empty" ejb-jar.xml files as to keep them as small as possible impressing what we mean by having an empty ejb-jar.xml.
